<h2 id="11august1994">Update 227G # Date 11 August 1994</h2>
<p>CHAPTER 27 - DETERMINING RATES OF PAYMENT - Assessment of investment income - debentures and unsecured notes. See guidelines 27.11600 to 27.11603.</p>
<p>Deferred interest debentures purchased before 1 January 1988 are assessed on realisation. All non-deferred interest debentures are assessed on an ongoing basis, regardless of the purchase date. Any debenture purchased before 20 September 1990 is not subject to the deeming rules.</p>
